c: 40
v: 78
t: Rasul dum dilee ka Kamoe kirem Teuma nyang ladom ka Kamoe peugah Nyang ladom hana Kamoe peuhaba Keunan bak gata hana meukisah Teuma di rasul ‘oh geuba ayat Bandum nyan meuhat ngon izin Allah Oh watee ka troh peurintah Tuhan Bandum putusan hana soe ubah Putusan Tuhan beuna ade that Yohnyan rugoe that awak nyang salah Nyang pubuet bateu raya that rugoe